| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2358 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhouse)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ddb5e433-0d1d-5057-96fe-ba6802fe6562"
